description:
Bjarne Stroustrup - GSL ad hoc overview - Meeting C++ 2016

Bjarne did an ad-hoc presentation about the Guideline Support Library at Meeting C++ 2016.
This talk originally would have been about the GSL tooling of Peter Sommerlad, who unfortunately couldn't attend the conference.
Thanks to Bjarne Stroustrup for doing a last minute, ad-hoc presentation on the GSL and its goals.
title: Bjarne Stroustrup - GSL ad hoc overview - Meeting C++ 2016
